org.unisens

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.unisens.Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    An Event happens at a cetain point in time and be of a certain type. It can have a comment. Events have no signal or value data.
